snippet.title: Despacito (Multi-Language Cover) 1 Guy Singing in 20 Different Languages - Travys Kim
snippet.description:
Hey, Travengers! Here’s my multi-language version of “Despacito” by Luis Fonsi (ft. Daddy Yankee). It’s been a while since this song came out but it’s such a great song and I just had to cover it. Please use your earphones/headphones for better quality and if you liked this video, don’t forget to give it a BIG THUMBS UP, SHARE and SUBSCRIBE! It means the world to me. Thanks! ;)

* Here’s the list of 20 languages I sang in:

Swahili – Portuguese – French – Arabic – Korean – Polish – Chinese – Filipino – Japanese – Spanish – Italian – Bahasa Indonesia – Bahasa Malaysia – Tamil – Thai – Russian – English – German – Finnish – Vietnamese 

* I do not own the song so please support the official release.

#Despacito #MultiLanguage #TravysKim #despacitocover #LuisFonsi #DaddyYankee #JustinBieber
